Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.10,0:00:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.00,0:00:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.68,0:00:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.62,0:00:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.36,0:00:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.26,0:00:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.90,0:00:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.31,0:00:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.34,0:01:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.48,0:01:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.95,0:01:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.32,0:01:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.10,0:01:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.53,0:01:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.97,0:01:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.03,0:01:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.16,0:01:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.59,0:02:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.56,0:02:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩三天來都沒有露臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.33,0:02:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#18 響子的禮物\N咦!這個要送給我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.31,0:02:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是房租
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是伙食費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.42,0:02:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,如果是吃\N“站著吃蕎麥麵”解決的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.52,0:02:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來,生活費支出應該是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這些應該就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.38,0:03:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.91,0:03:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要參加茶茶丸的派對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰要去參加派對啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.89,0:03:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹教練說他要來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.66,0:03:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然管理員也會來囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.40,0:03:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.74,0:03:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬妳美麗的瞳眸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.79,0:03:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.66,0:04:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這麼說的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.60,0:04:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話,你也會來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.37,0:04:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五點開始喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.74,0:04:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下2488圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼夠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.58,0:04:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆不要送禮物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.62,0:04:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.66,0:04:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠公然送禮物的\N只有聖誕節而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.99,0:04:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便宜也沒關係\N最重要的是誠意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.39,0:04:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定會明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.20,0:04:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,今天就去買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.40,0:04:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,管理員到底是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.24,0:04:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.77,0:04:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來…來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.64,0:04:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.79,0:05:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很吵耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.46,0:05:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N至少讓我看一下背影會怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.60,0:05:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,小津江啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.57,0:05:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天?好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.07,0:05:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛好要出去買東西\N買完後再跟妳見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.84,0:05:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那待會見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸\N不要這樣光明正大偷聽好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是女朋友打來的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.55,0:05:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不用從二樓奮力衝下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.99,0:05:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話又不會跑掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.13,0:05:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話是不會跑掉沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.26,0:05:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話是不會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.77,0:05:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想見管理員的話\N就去敲她的門啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.94,0:05:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒什麼事找她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找個藉口不就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要稍微學習一下\N三鷹教練的厚臉皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾,我天生害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是沒志氣而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒出息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.60,0:06:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,居然說我沒志氣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就讓妳看看我的志氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.16,0:06:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出門了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.38,0:07:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.41,0:07:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也只有聲音而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.97,0:08:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛好花了兩千圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天又要過苦日子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.91,0:08:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,船到橋頭自然直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.15,0:08:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,這樣就有理由\N去敲管理員的門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個要送給我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.16,0:08:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以打開來看嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好漂亮的耳環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.55,0:08:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他又在撞電線桿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底在幹什麼啊?\N真是個怪胎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.39,0:08:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得改改我的幻想症才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.99,0:09:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.70,0:09:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,我來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.10,0:09:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的額頭怎麼了?流血了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.47,0:09:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,我拿手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.21,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,我用自己的手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請給我一杯美式咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.86,0:09:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.89,0:09:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天找我有什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然早了一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.23,0:09:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.24,0:09:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.05,0:09:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帽子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.18,0:09:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然織得不太好\N不過是我親手織的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴戴看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.09,0:09:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.42,0:10:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好帥,好帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.56,0:10:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有把小津江的份算進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.47,0:10:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,既然已經收了人家的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.04,0:10:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.44,0:10:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是要送給我的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.54,0:10:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.15,0:10:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以打開來看嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.31,0:10:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請…請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,是耳環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好成熟喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.49,0:11:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會…會嗎?妳戴起來很好看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.90,0:11:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,我真的好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.96,0:11:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到妳這麼高興,我也很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.23,0:11:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,我是白痴嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.53,0:11:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種優柔寡斷的個性\N難道到死也改不了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.04,0:12:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好溫暖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.38,0:12:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,我真的好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江真的好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.32,0:12:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然高興成那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.86,0:12:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,這樣就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.34,0:12:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.74,0:12:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是只有聲音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.75,0:12:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.19,0:12:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.93,0:12:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,真的好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這三天來是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.14,0:13:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.68,0:13:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忙著編織圍巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.55,0:13:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說,這是要送給我的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你喜不喜歡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.79,0:13:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當…當然喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.36,0:13:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先失陪了,我想去補個眠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.63,0:13:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為連續熬夜都沒睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳熬夜織圍巾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.70,0:13:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.04,0:13:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳的圍巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.41,0:13:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.62,0:13:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.46,0:14:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,我好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.20,0:14:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禮物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.10,0:14:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有禮物可以送管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.12,0:14:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今把房租拿出來用…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.99,0:14:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,不可以用房租
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.59,0:14:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房租付不出來\N反而會給管理員添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.16,0:14:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,伙食費…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.97,0:14:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是四、五天不吃\N應該死不了才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.98,0:15:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總不能叫她還我吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.09,0:15:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,我真的好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.19,0:15:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,我真的好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員送了一條圍巾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.51,0:15:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且聽說是熬夜三天親手織的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.38,0:15:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還用上好的毛線耶\N圍起來很溫暖喔,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看,讓我也圍圍看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這樣拉啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.02,0:15:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,這是我的寶貝圍巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.19,0:15:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼態度啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.83,0:15:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你也過來喝嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.84,0:16:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年終大掃除,現在還太早啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟妳說過不要拉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.55,0:16:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在在找東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.82,0:16:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了,請不要吵我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.02,0:16:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪了\N我記得放在這個抽屜裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.36,0:16:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.29,0:16:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到一張准考證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.67,0:16:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.31,0:16:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了一年了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.94,0:16:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重考生時代真的很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.48,0:16:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片也一臉苦惱的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.35,0:16:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼神黯然無光\N一付鬧彆扭的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.55,0:16:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當然會變得灰暗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.79,0:16:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那時候被你們當作白痴耍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.33,0:16:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也一樣被當作白痴耍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.09,0:17:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的身分沒有變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.90,0:17:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是一刻館的玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.63,0:17:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之東西找到了,恭喜你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,喝酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.61,0:17:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是!我要找的不是那個!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.32,0:17:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.29,0:17:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,妳也回自己的房間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.96,0:17:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.43,0:17:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會趁妳睡覺時侵犯妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.29,0:17:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有種你就試試看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.04,0:17:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然睡得這麼安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到一百圓!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.68,0:17:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴,一百圓能幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.67,0:18:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.50,0:18:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼睡相嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.63,0:18:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找不到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.66,0:18:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.92,0:19:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個要送給我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.16,0:19:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思沒有包裝起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.49,0:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.49,0:19:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛的別針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.43,0:19:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳喜歡這個別針嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.97,0:19:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.54,0:19:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛好像很紅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我昨晚熬夜沒睡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會睡到傍晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡得好飽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.53,0:19:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.97,0:19:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這條圍巾好溫暖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.61,0:20:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,跟帽子也很合喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.58,0:20:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳戴這個別針也很好看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還適合這麼可愛的東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.92,0:20:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼話,妳明明還很年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.66,0:20:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是,我也才22歲而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,22歲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.60,0:20:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大我兩歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.47,0:20:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才大我兩歲而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.81,0:20:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這應該不會造成結婚的障礙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.61,0:20:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才差兩歲而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.08,0:20:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.35,0:20:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代也要去茶茶丸的派對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.15,0:20:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.92,0:20:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那正好,一起走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.96,0:20:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,想不到你蠻怕冷的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.57,0:20:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明這麼年輕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.00,0:21:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,這條圍巾好溫暖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.27,0:21:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是管理員用真心親手織的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.71,0:21:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這是音無小姐親手織的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.05,0:21:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.65,0:21:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活該,看你能說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.82,0:21:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點冷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.70,0:21:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.80,0:21:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐親手織的圍巾\N真的很溫暖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.28,0:21:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,織同樣的圍巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.38,0:21:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我只有這點本事而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.28,0:21:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.55,0:21:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顏色織得不同\N這點妳實在太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.12,0:21:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果以為自己特別\N就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.16,0:21:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過\N送同樣的圍巾是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.63,0:22:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是腳踏兩條船?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.43,0:22:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是我跟五代是同等級的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.27,0:22:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟哪裡做的不好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.91,0:22:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.75,0:22:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳的圍巾,好溫暖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.82,0:22:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.96,0:22:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,謝啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.26,0:22:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的用心真的好溫暖\N讓我打從心裡暖和起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.83,0:22:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個披肩好溫暖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.50,0:22:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為上次我腳扭傷\N受到大家的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.44,0:22:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是一點心意兼聖誕節禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.74,0:22:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連我爸爸\N管理員都幫他織了一條圍巾喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.75,0:22:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為一家三口都有比較好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.69,0:23:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老公高興到\N連眼淚都流出來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.44,0:23:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的圍巾花樣都一樣耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.14,0:23:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.01,0:23:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,因為時間不夠\N所以大家都織一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.32,0:23:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說,就算花樣一樣\N但是顏色不一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.92,0:23:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,也幫我織一條吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.56,0:23:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.73,0:23:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.21,0:23:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三更半夜的一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.87,0:23:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一片寂靜之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.71,0:23:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一對男女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.75,0:24:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得哪來的鐘聲響個不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.75,0:24:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.42,0:24:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「五代和響子!\N倆人的夜晚充滿危險」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.92,0:24:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?\N希望不會有事發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.91,0:24:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天在陌生的城市下了一場陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.68,0:24:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳非常在意淋溼的高跟鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.82,0:24:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從前妳用那隱藏著\N稚氣的側臉和我交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.73,0:24:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的話語至今仍能想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.81,0:25:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就彷佛\N置身電影中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.68,0:25:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳輕聲細語地說著\N安靜的最後一幕
